Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:58.76,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, I heard \Na terrible noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:01:58.76,Sign,LETTER,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mashiro-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:02.60,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. This is how it works...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:05.08,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I heard something \Nsnapping inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.08,0:02:07.95,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The world isn't fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:10.37,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,My body creaked...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:14.87,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much I want to \Ncatch up, it's still not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:14.87,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I felt like my heart \Nwas being ripped in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:19.36,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we give it everything \Nwe have, it's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:22.12,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I could \Ndo to protect myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.73,0:02:24.60,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,was to take my pain \Nout on someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:26.70,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There was nothing we could do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:30.47,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to say those things,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:32.28,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:36.13,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:42.59,Sign,CALENDAR,0000,0000,0000,,Graduation Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:47.56,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}#22 Run Through Those Sparkling Days
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:02:56.40,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, kouhai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:02:59.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're up early, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:01.25,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,The graduation ceremony's today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:02.57,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's show some enthusiasm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:07.49,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The graduation ceremony \Nreally is happening today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:11.41,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Misaki. I'll come after \NI have something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.41,0:03:12.46,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:15.93,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You should wake Mashiro-chan soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:17.63,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't have time \Nfor breakfast otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:19.43,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have that, kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:22.88,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Food is the source of our power! \NLet's stuff ourselves silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:30.09,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun looks down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:32.43,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we've got to keep it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:33.98,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:37.11,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiron's Room
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:37.11,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Please Knock
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:41.59,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:44.30,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:46.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.20,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:54.69,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:56.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:04:00.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you're not, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:02.97,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I feel a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:04.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:06.40,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to remember how \NI looked when I was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:07.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Because you looked grody?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:10.64,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like you when you call girls ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:18.53,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could forget about \Nwhat happened yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:22.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could relive yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.19,0:04:24.01,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:27.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Forget I said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:31.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I've got to wake Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:32.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:35.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:37.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina, I'm opening the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.91,0:04:41.34,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Get up, Shii—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:46.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:51.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:58.18,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's wrong, Kanda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:02.86,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro left this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:05.53,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:08.74,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall is being torn \Ndown because of Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.38,0:05:11.02,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:14.02,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why didn't you stop her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:22.76,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I asked her if she talked it over with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:30.28,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,When she first arrived at Sakura Hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:33.30,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,she wouldn't have cared how you felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:37.89,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you all, Mashiro has changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:41.07,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's for the \Nworse in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:43.57,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:46.40,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Her GPS says she's at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.24,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro-sama: Locked on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:49.57,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.22,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:52.41,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:53.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:54.80,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:56.09,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I going, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:56.75,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:02.75,Sign,LETTER,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mashiro-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:08.43,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,29th Suimei University of the Arts \NHigh School Graduation Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:11.35,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiron!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:12.78,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:15.74,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,30 meters to Mashiro-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:17.41,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,30 meters? In which direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:19.81,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,That's the art room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.81,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,All out dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:26.03,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:32.94,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mashiro's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.67,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Did Mashiro-chan paint this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.57,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,She must have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:45.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Is this me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:46.96,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:48.63,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,And the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:51.66,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:53.66,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,She really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:06:58.25,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Not even...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:03.67,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Not even the most...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:06.81,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,famous painters throughout history\Ncould have painted this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:13.51,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This painting is the love \NMashiro feels for Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:16.70,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:19.33,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.26,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you the only one missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:26.00,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But that's why I understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:28.86,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.80,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Just how strongly Mashiro felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:34.30,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,when she said those words that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:39.29,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro-chan planned to \Nprotect Sakura Hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:41.60,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,by leaving if we failed to \Nget enough signatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:43.18,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:45.77,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the Sakura Hall I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:51.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of goodbye is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:52.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point if it ends like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:53.70,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:56.97,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, Sorata, \Nyou'll have to tell her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:01.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:05.85,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Operation: Search for Mashiron begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:07.54,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing Mashiro-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:10.10,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,it's unlikely she's returned \Nto England on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:12.71,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Has she ever even ridden a train by herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:15.89,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check out places in the \Narea Mashiro might visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai and Jin-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:19.97,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,search the school and \Nthe surrounding area.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:20.78,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:22.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll search the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.52,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.30,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you're back for \Nthe graduation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:30.46,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm determined to get you to give \Nme the most magnificent send-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:32.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring Mashiro back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:36.32,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look for her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:38.02,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:42.12,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll search around \NSakura Hall just in case, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:50.66,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, you take the area from \Nthe shopping mall to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:52.64,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll check the area around \Nthe convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:53.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Call me if you find Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:03.68,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:12.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:18.00,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Your promise to listen to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:20.27,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,what I had to say once I got the \Nresults of my audition...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:22.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:24.96,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:28.81,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I've always... always...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.05,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been grateful \NI got to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:35.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:39.97,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I've been able to work so hard \Nup to now because you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:42.95,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at your face gave me energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:45.48,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing your voice made me optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:49.52,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Before I knew it, I was \Nalways watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:54.20,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing you compliment my clothes \Nand hair made my feelings soar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:56.32,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,The days we talked a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:58.78,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,made me feel like I could \Ntry that much harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:03.72,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:09.23,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for giving me \Nthe will to work so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:12.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:13.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Because of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:15.01,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I know. That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:19.76,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You should tell Mashiro how you feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:24.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:31.19,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I've been able \Nto work so hard until today...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:34.83,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,is because I'm in love \Nwith you, Kanda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:39.11,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.21,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiron!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:42.37,Sign,PACKAGE,0000,0000,0000,,Baumkuchen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:44.13,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Did the girl who always \Nbuys these come in today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:46.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:52.52,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Searching on foot is ineffective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:54.12,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I doing this, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:57.23,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,How can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:00.49,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Send an email to the former freeloader.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:04.46,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"Shiina felt responsible for Sakura \NHall being torn down and ran off."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.46,0:11:06.67,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,"Do you have any idea where \Nshe might have gone?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:08.07,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,Request received.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.06,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming Call
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.06,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Former Freeloader
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:14.41,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.10,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,That's your first question?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:17.90,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural for \Nme to be suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.55,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,since this isn't an international call.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:21.07,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Where could I be, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:23.88,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,A hologram?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:25.54,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Want to touch me and find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:26.71,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:30.75,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,That's no way to treat someone \Nwho was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:33.33,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't patronize me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:36.27,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there something \Nyou'd like to say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:37.96,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:40.20,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:41.64,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:43.47,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:47.05,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,When you emailed me \Nsaying you wanted to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:48.43,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,something for Jin and Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.10,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:53.64,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I like how you can't admit your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:56.49,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,E-Enough of your jokes! \NLet's look for Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:58.44,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:11:59.70,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.01,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro doesn't give up so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:04.51,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,on something once she's \Ndecided she wants it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:07.32,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Despite how she looks,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:12.12,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,she's actually the world's most \Nselfish and stubborn sore loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:13.46,Sign,GARBAGE,0000,0000,0000,,Burnable
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:20.05,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Someone already came asking \Nme to subscribe to the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:21.97,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:26.14,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What a warm welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:28.20,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:30.39,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't act so immaturely \Nin front of children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:32.83,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I came to apologize for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:35.73,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I feel badly about what \NI did to Kanda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:41.15,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,No one told me another team \Nwas trying to hire Shiina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:42.88,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,No matter the circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:45.52,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't doing something about it your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:47.36,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:49.08,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:51.87,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,This place hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:55.16,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,And your habit of ignoring \Neverything you don't want to hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:56.77,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,hasn't changed, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:58.94,Saku-overlap,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they were going \Nto tear Sakura Hall down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:01.09,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What did I just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:03.23,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything I can do to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.43,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:05.79,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there were, \Nwe don't need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:06.59,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:10.49,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,They'll do something about it themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:15.48,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:18.47,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I even checked around the college, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:22.04,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go look outside the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.04,0:13:22.61,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:27.20,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,They left us at school so we wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:29.35,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,be late to our graduation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:30.89,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Let's trust them with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:32.75,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there's something \Nwe have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:34.81,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:37.68,Saku-main,HAUHAU,0000,0000,0000,,You two always get along so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:40.97,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Not as well as you two, \Nwho we always see together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:43.26,Saku-main,HAUHAU,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:44.42,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:46.77,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,For you. It's a love letter from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:48.89,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to look at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:51.10,Saku-main,PRESIDENT,0000,0000,0000,,If you're serious, \Nthere's no need to read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:54.84,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Hau-hau, your boyfriend is so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:57.06,Saku-main,HAUHAU,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:14:00.09,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Just as we planned, Mr. Former \NStudent Council President.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:01.63,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:05.08,Saku-main,PRESIDENT,0000,0000,0000,,If you're really sorry, \Ndon't get me involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:06.90,Saku-main,HAUHAU,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki, you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:10.20,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to \Nyour video, Hau-hau.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:12.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:15.04,Saku-main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Kanda's boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Mashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:19.99,Saku-main,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,She was heading towards the \Nstation about ten minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:21.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:24.51,Saku-main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on, \Nbut you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:25.92,Saku-main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Youth is for exploding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:28.88,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought it was kinda boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:31.68,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,that every day was the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:36.29,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I pretended it was someone \Nelse's fault that nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:41.18,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But when I met Mashiro \Nthat fall, I realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:43.61,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,that if you put your mind to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:45.69,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,you can change the color of \Nthe world in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:55.60,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:57.37,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What color do you want to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.61,0:15:00.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:02.33,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:10.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:14.59,Saku-main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:15.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay later!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:19.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:23.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:24.44,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:26.09,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:28.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Because you suddenly disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.86,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,But Sakura Hall will \Nbe torn down if I stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:34.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care! It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:35.15,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:38.48,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the graduation ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.75,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but we didn't fill the whole notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:42.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:44.80,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,We have to fill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:45.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:48.50,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:52.38,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I worked hard, but Sakura \NHall will be torn down...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:56.62,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of me! I hurt you, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:16:00.06,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You hate me. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:01.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:05.10,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to stay at Sakura \NHall if it will make you hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:07.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't. I don't hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:07.95,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:09.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Just listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:25.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I think what I said \Nyesterday was how I really feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:33.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'd been thinking it \Nfor a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:39.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I was jealous of you because \Nyou had everything I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:42.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered, "why is it always you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:44.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I was so frustrated,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:47.23,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I almost thought I hated you sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:52.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:56.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Because of you, I was \Nable to find my own goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:17:01.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I worked hard, but I failed \Nand was disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:05.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But all of that made for \Nthe greatest of days!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:10.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't met you, I never \Nwould have known these feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:16.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I love you for \Nteaching me all of these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:17.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:20.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:22.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:50.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:53.12,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:55.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:58.14,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:01.18,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:04.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:05.96,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay at Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:07.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:10.82,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,But if I stay, \NSakura Hall will be torn down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:15.65,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cause everyone else \Ntrouble, and I'll hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You can hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:23.49,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I made Nanami endure so \Nmuch after the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.38,0:18:29.40,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to stay at Sakura \NHall if it will hurt someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:31.30,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:32.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:35.71,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act like my \Nfrustration is your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:40.22,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Failing the audition is my own problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:41.74,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:44.46,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,This experience is all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:45.54,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:48.00,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Ignoring Kanda-kun's warnings...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:51.27,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretending I was fine \Nwere my own decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:55.15,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't feel responsible for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:58.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Aoyama. You don't \Nhave to be so harsh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:18:59.28,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:01.54,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami, are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:03.69,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like I'm {\i1}not{\i0} mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:06.69,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,But, Mashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:09.92,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really happy you \Nwere worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:12.75,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.19,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:15.81,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:21.64,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,So I won't let you just leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:22.86,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:25.70,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:31.50,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,But it's my fault Sakura Hall \Nis going to be torn down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:34.52,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go, but I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.43,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,We told you, you don't have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:40.94,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:41.99,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:44.10,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,My chest hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:45.66,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I always feel terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.53,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:51.00,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:58.26,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, if there's anything you \Nwant to say, you can tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:02.26,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Just because she's crying, \Nshe's not going to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:04.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:08.12,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're powerless against \NMashiro's tears, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:14.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:15.67,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:19.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand Sakura Hall at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:20.59,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:21.88,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:22.74,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:27.91,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The Sakura Hall I'm talking about \Nisn't that rundown building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:33.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sakura Hall because \NMisaki-senpai and Jin-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:36.96,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama and Chihiro-sensei, \NAkasaka and you are there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:39.38,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:42.13,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sakura Hall because \Neveryone is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:45.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, what I'm \Ntrying to say is—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:45.98,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:47.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:51.88,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Sakura Hall is Sakura Hall \Nbecause everyone is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:53.23,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,We're all Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:55.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:20:58.52,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always stay at Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:01.98,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:06.03,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:09.95,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You said I made you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:11.29,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:13.46,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:14.79,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:17.71,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:20.72,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:23.88,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait. That hurts, Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:24.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:26.83,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be okay, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:28.44,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:30.73,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:32.95,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but you should probably \Nhead to school soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:33.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:34.86,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Rita?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:36.23,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:37.63,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:38.73,Saku-main,NANANMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:41.81,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,The graduation ceremony is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.81,0:21:42.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:43.50,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.50,0:21:44.29,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:45.00,Saku-overlap,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Ryunosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:45.00,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:46.36,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:47.69,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:48.41,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:51.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't know what \Ncolor I want to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:53.62,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but today is a specific color.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:57.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Even if today's the last \Nday we're all together,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.22,0:21:59.08,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want the graduation ceremony to \Nbe the color of cherry blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:09.27,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I love the color of cherry blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:32.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Graduation!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.54,0:23:33.66,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Graduation!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.66,0:23:35.21,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Laughing with everyone \Nat the culture festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.87,0:23:40.98,NextEptitle,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}#23 Graduation Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.21,0:23:36.71,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Running at the pool \Nwith everyone at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.71,0:23:38.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to graduate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.66,0:23:40.07,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda, why are {\i1}you{\i0} running?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.07,0:23:40.98,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Come back!
